openmediavault-vmmanager (1.0.0) stable; urgency=low

  * Initial release of the OMV 8 plugin for omv-vmmanager.
  * Wraps the Go backend (libvirt/KVM VM management) as a native
    OMV service with confdb integration, Salt state, and workbench
    UI (navigation, settings form, embedded UI page, dashboard widget).
  * Auth bridge: pre-shared API key persists in
    /etc/openmediavault-vmmanager/apikey.key.
  * Reverse-proxy at /vmmanager/ via nginx so the webUI is embeddable
    in an iframe inside the OMV workbench.

 -- omv-vmmanager <alvinpp1908@gmail.com>  Sat, 29 Jun 2026 18:00:00 +0200
